snippet.title: Minecraft - Fallout Mash-Up
snippet.description: Welcome to the Wasteland! Celebrate the Fallout® series in Minecraft by cracking open this Vault containing 44 unique skins, custom textures, re-skinned mobs, a special post-apocalyptic map, original Fallout soundtrack compilation and a Pip-Boy inspired UI.
